sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭下的士，行下街市先啦，港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n離地離到咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒到唔撚敢睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當八達通近乎壟斷，到今日仲不斷擴展佢嘅板圖，我真係唔知係邊個柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭的士我就寧願Uber算啦<br />\n用電子付款嘅之後會連八折的都冇埋<br />\n其他我寧願佢發展俾我用paywave、tapngo、payme嗰啲好過<br />\n依啲起碼發展潛力大，幅蓋範圍大<br />\n橫掂香港都冇晒細鋪㗎啦，用visa master把啦，去到外國又用得"},{"pid":"aa5dd318da45dbd6675d7c3090ef5f399d9b1290","tid":350159,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"又applepau又androidpay<br />\n係部份人係要拉落支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4663323cd85c12e9964dfdee5eed5cf995dc92c","tid":350159,"uid":64290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"樓上有巴打話唔可以p2p<br />\n事實上八達通個app已經做緊呢樣野"},{"pid":"a4d6bef2ed659eb0d60265bee31bc67eaae48511","tid":350159,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"落後論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係香港人根本唔多鐘意用e-payment<br />\n或者咁講,佢地唔相信e-payment<br />\n你見香港年年都有人交紙張版既報稅表就知咩料啦<br />\n轉用e-tax又唔洗比手續費<br />\n<br />\n事例證實香港人係好保守 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你見放工時間仲係鬼死咁多人去ATM轉帳/禁錢<br />\n去大家樂/麥當勞仲係好多人比Cash<br />\n<br />\n香港拎Cash太方便,唔似得其他地方<br />\n而且假鈔真係算少, 冇乜動力去推d人用"},{"pid":"254b6bffc03eed44f3c14d46ac70c002fc669f93","tid":350159,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又applepau又androidpay<br />\n係部份人係要拉落支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地話要租機同埋要搭的士喎<br />\n佢地唔洗擔心，多得政府，我地好快冇晒細鋪㗎啦<br />\n而的士我亦寧願搭Uber"},{"pid":"9